attachments.title: Google Integrates Food Ordering Into Search Results For Restaurants
attachments.text: Google now lets users in the U.S. order food from six companies—Seamless, Grubhub, Eat24, <http://Delivery.com|Delivery.com>, BeyondMenu, and <http://MyPizza.com|MyPizza.com>—directly from search results.
